---
title: Creamy Chicken Breast and Mushroom Filo Pie with Carrot and Onion
description: A twist on a puff pastry or mash topped pie, using scrunches of filo pastry to crown the creamy filling results in a golden and crispy top. Here, we're giving homage to the classic chicken and mushroom pie.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W38_UK_R10512-6_Main_low_2-dc909006.jpg
